家盡快無限期三罷</span><br />\n<br />\n我會支持三罷，亦會身體力行一齊三罷保護香港，直至港府落實封關<br />\n<br />\n香港人以及醫護、海關等要職唔一齊三罷嘅後果，只會鼓勵更多支那感染者衝嚟香港求醫，間接促成社區爆發，害死包括醫護同海關全家在內嘅更多人大家唔通想犧牲香港200萬手足同自己全家條命去救呢d準備落地獄嘅人渣？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「感染的人越多越好」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fEievG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fEievG.jpg&h=ea5edc6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">把我臉上的口罩撕下來朝我吐了口吐沫，說「我活不了，你們都別想活」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COPqDXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOPqDXm.jpg&h=e479048d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">撕扯她們的防護服「要死一起死」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ3Gchn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ3Gchn.jpg&h=8f4e3e83&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"529222e9e71a307fe8f9126aabba7ad7135ff1d1","tid":1847941,"uid":103842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:10:55.000Z","msg":"用禮賓府側邊個醫院做隔離中心啦<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母林鄭</span></span>"},{"pid":"990f21c4c6ed58cb64ede07edb9624c7547e2b6b","tid":1847941,"uid":266755,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"好老實03年時除了支人外，醫管局話有疑似發燒但不嚴重個案都喺自家隔離自己量體溫，唔喺嚴重盡量避免去醫院，避免交叉感染。<br />\n都喺同一套話。"},{"pid":"7b879c62e9b09be1f2d54f60a93132ecfa56b8bf","tid":1847941,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"邊界本來就係我哋人民委托政府去管理，依家佢管理不善，我哋就接管關口！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847865</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2519cf468d9b897507b05c2a51e5a548d2b29609","tid":1847941,"uid":35580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"大大間港中醫院唔用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550005b888446796932d2c5466779e8a67c